{
  "id": "adv_main_03_07_04",
  "title": "BIG4編1章34話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……琴乃？　琴乃か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Kotono? Is that you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 3.3961225271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "あ……っ\n{user}、さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…!\n{user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 9.3761226415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "……いろいろと、急に事を進めてしまってすみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’m sorry for suddenly making things move forward like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.3761226415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……どりきゅんの事務所に移籍するとは聞いていたけど\nまさか二人と一緒に行動していたとはな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I heard you were transferring to DoriKyun’s agency‚\nbut I never thought you’d be working with them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.0999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 20.3704307796
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "申し遅れました。私は星見プロのマネージャーを\nしております。よろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ I haven't introduced myself.\nI'm {user}‚ the manager of Hoshimi Pro. Nice to meet you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4729948822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-lmn001.m4a",
      "text": "どうも、ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.3770974082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 29.2290022455
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-lmn002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃、あなたの元マネージャーでしょう？\nちゃんと状況を説明しておいた方がいいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ this is your former manager‚ right?\nShouldn't you explain the situation properly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.133333397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……はい、分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ I understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.6617458267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_unrest-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 39.3591607334
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 39.3591607334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "私は今、アイドルとしての強さを学ぶために……\nれもんさんと来夢さんに同行させてもらってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m currently accompanying Lemon-san and Laim-san…\nto learn what it means to be strong as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5179814976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "同行……今日の挨拶回りもその一環、という訳か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Accompanying… So today’s greetings are a part of that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8948977075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 53.1648987058
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-lim001.m4a",
      "text": "ったく、ただでさえめんどくせぇのに\nなんでこいつの面倒まで見なきゃいけねぇんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Geez‚ this is already a pain in the ass‚\nwhy do I have to take care of her too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.43333416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-lmn003.m4a",
      "text": "先輩面したいなら、もっと挨拶をきっちりやりなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you want to act like a senior‚ greet people properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.9801366731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 64.9482113445
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "今後は練習も一緒にやらせてもらう予定です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m also planning to do training with them from now on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.9482113445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……そうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3201357925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 69.7204517448
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 69.7204517448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "私は……この決断が間違っていたとは思いません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… don’t think this decision was wrong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7204517448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 74.5567373995
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "月ストから離れないと得られなかったものが\nいくつもありました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are many things that I couldn't have gained\nwithout leaving Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.6346282325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "あのまま五人で活動を続けていたら……\nきっと動けなくなっていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we had continued our activities with five members…\nI would have been paralyzed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8012933733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 85.0387716375
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "……だから、私は、その……もう、星見プロには……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ I… I’m no longer with Hoshimi Pro…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.0387716375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 92.8975018266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "なんにせよ、琴乃が元気そうで良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I'm glad you’re doing well‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.8975018266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 96.6423316403
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.6423316403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tears-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 97.9137158834
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、琴乃のことを心配してたからな。もちろん俺も",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone was worried about you‚ Kotono. Me too‚ of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.9137158834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 102.5977974378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃が今そこに……どりきゅんのお二人の隣に\n立っているのは、沢山悩んだ結果だと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ for you to be standing there… next to the DoriKyun…\nI believe that’s the result of a lot of agonizing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.075928446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "その覚悟を否定したりはしないよ。何より、辛い決断を\nさせてしまったのは俺の責任だ……本当にすまなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won’t deny your resolve; after all‚ it’s my responsibility\nthat you had to make such a difficult decision… I’m truly sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.8420139753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 120.3612204992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}、さん……私、私……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san… I… I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.3612204992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 126.8868666931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_04-lim002.m4a",
      "text": "おい、琴乃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.8868666931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
